{"tid":1476234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【獻策】818召集的心理策略","createTime":"2019-08-15T17:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T09:49:36.000Z","uid":305360,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"000edd4fc2ae2e4a82603538f0f77d2666e93f14","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T17:59:55.000Z","msg":"今晚成晚，我棟高床板，諗到呢個方法。主要係從心理學角度，推動各位圈子既人出黎。各位巴打絲打，睇下做唔做到，行唔行得通。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係內文。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">生死存亡</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n818大遊行的重要性毋庸置疑，將會是整場運動的關鍵時刻。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">謠言四起，恐嚇不絕。解放軍入城、黑社會蠢蠢欲動、機場苦肉計、黑警拒批不反對通知書</span></span></strong>予遊行等等，政府務求壓縮集會人數。<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果集會人數遜色於69、612，運動將難以為繼</span></span></strong>。故此，我們<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">必須集合所有人站出來，匯聚一切力量</span></strong></span>，發出不平之鳴，讓全世界聽到！每個人都重要，所有黃絲都必定要出來，並且要拉攏召集身邊全部的中立游離派，一起走向維園。但是，我們要如何說服中立游離派？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攻心為上</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一般人做決定時會依賴以下兩個模型的其中一個：結果模型(Consequence Model)或者身份模型(Identity Model)。<br />\n<br />\n結果模型(Consequence Model)以理性為主，例如思考送中條例帶來的弊端、雙普選對香港的益處等等，用利弊好壞作決策依據。然而，人並非全然理性，藍屍的存在清楚證明這一點。很多時候，人做決定時是不自覺的，帶有情緒，受制於潛意識。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">身份模型(Identity Model)揭示實質影響人的判斷主要是身份認知。</span></strong></span>「我是誰？」「跟我一樣身份的人在做什麼？」這些問題在心裡無聲地發揮著作用。心理學家Jessica Nolan於2003年在加州做實驗，把四種不同的門把掛牌分派給372戶人家，測試掛牌內容對用戶省電的影響力。其中三種內容分別圍繞「保護環境」、「為下一代節能」及「省電省錢」等理念。研究顯示收到這三種掛牌的家庭用電量變化微乎其微，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只有收到第四種掛牌的家庭有顯著改善&mdash;&mdash;「你的鄰居都在節能」。（即係話，要比我地社交圈子既人知道，我地會出黎！！！）</span></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n在遊說中立游離派時，痛陳利弊難收其效。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重要的是運用社會認同(Social Proof)，喚醒他的身份認同。</span></strong></span>我們生活在許多小圈子裡，例如求學階段認識的小圈子、職場上的小圈子，乃至閒暇行山結織的小圈子。每個小圈子都是一個部落(Tribe)，個體會追隨著部落的步伐。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在這些小圈子裡的中立派便是我們要遊說的對象，說服小圈子的人比說服陌生人容易百倍。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我們要把參加818塑造成部落的大趨勢：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">小圈子裡大多數人都出席，你呢？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n假設小圈子有七人，三名黃絲（Amy、Chris、Ray)，四名中立(Doris、May、David、Peter)。我們需要名單。可以用whatsapp聯絡Doris，展示給她看818出席者有Amy、Chris、Ray，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">看她要不要一起去香港人救香港人</span></strong></span>。當Doris答應，便加入名單，用這份名單再說服下一位。營造小圈子裡大多數人都參加的跡象，逐一遊說。<br />\n<br />\n不用說服對方成為黃絲，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們要喚醒的是對方已潛在的身份認同&mdash;&mdash;「我是這群人的朋友（所以我會參與）」、「我是香港人（所以會出來拯救我城）」</span></span></strong>。遊說完後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在群組裡列出名單</span></strong></span>，定下集合時間地點，正正式式（出黎做d合法既野，例如野餐散步），並且要Personal Touch地<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">稱讚一下肯出黎既人</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">「我記得David有次在旺角制止個醉酒鬼打人，極之正直。今次警察濫權濫暴到咁，難怪忍唔住要企出黎！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n登門檻效應(Foot In The Door Effect)之所以有效，就是因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">人會去盡量保持一致的正面形象</span></strong></span>。同理，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">稱讚的目的是令他知道自己在他人心中建立了正面形象，為了保持形象一致，818時就不會無故缺席</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp、Facebook上面，甚至instagram，大家都可以嘗試用身份模型的方法去召集身邊的游離派。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">名單越長，大家睇到，就越安心出黎。士氣就會如同滾雪球咁樣，越黎越高。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">一d本來因為工作關係（政府工、中資企業）唔敢出黎遊行，見到份長長既名單，就算口裡說不，亦會因為大家同屬圈子，（就算戴口罩），都會行出黎支持！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟們，係時候動用你地既人脈，用各種方法，組織參與。818呢鋪唔輸得，和理非集會，要多過200萬人呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d441ae7907ebe085d80d8e81b195972e13b6cd","tid":1476234,"uid":248384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:05:55.000Z","msg":"阻你小小位置 唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n［建議8.18］<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舉起為我地發過聲既國家國旗</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476223</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">有恩不報非君子</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有仇不報柱為人</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n+幫推！"},{"pid":"5a766329a0ef244b04c171188fdb87e0b5b16764","tid":1476234,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:09:00.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a24813e9f6b0d9cad9ff061508ea85f422cc1791","tid":1476234,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:11:57.000Z","msg":"推8.16 8.18"},{"pid":"0455a51b0182cf3b70758c6a1fcdcf852ee7f7f4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:18:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc99db7df1b57758f55dcb0a3890bca5e0c9987","tid":1476234,"uid":199712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:20:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n只要可以令818多啲人上街<br />\n做乜都得<br />\n818 不見不散<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ubTWn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ubTWn6.jpg&h=a517dbec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewrs0PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fewrs0PH.jpg&h=d52f1ecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDPFBn4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDPFBn4.png&h=e183a230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9gwH24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9gwH24.jpg&h=8c4636dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"933ae48c08e518d58aad42ca3f4e1701aca3e3b2","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de5cd595ec544422e134f37449aef4f1ba85aba","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b20485f0d8c05690a1cfdd64136efd4993f979","tid":1476234,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818百萬人大遊行<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同69,616同等重要，代表場運動有民意受權<br />\n818唔夠人數 場運動就自然死亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以 依家開始全民投入宣傳工作<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站</span><br />\nfacebook instagram瘋狂轉貼文宣<br />\n文宣source: <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=cec103bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=0df7d984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a>"},{"pid":"e4a8cc9fd0ad5f35578bd31953de5e79914305a7","tid":1476234,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:37:38.000Z","msg":"寧鳴而死，不默而生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抱住攬炒嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0903ea95f283419f6babba03d5a93e3c2c1727d8","tid":1476234,"uid":207936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T19:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gmdcnS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gmdcnS.png&h=4e525c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifsPu9z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifsPu9z.png&h=20b6f201&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xg9m5HW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxg9m5HW.png&h=242608a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9994c5f5e13cf86de11de83d7740004cc4c3e24b","tid":1476234,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T21:14:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818， 正視警黑合作!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fsnWTPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfsnWTPj.jpg&h=35ffcc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳給10個人，祝 好人一生平安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XM7cp8O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXM7cp8O.jpg&h=81d78807&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43dce6f414d7021048182f2b04442bc2458f6ef2","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:58:02.000Z","msg":"理念要相同，方法可不一，大家幫忙推推。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7facfae51d50f9fe77a8109b9ba5a98542e66bb","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43dce6f414d7021048182f2b04442bc2458f6ef2","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd735f1682e392f9c82857f40752f1d978d1ffc4","tid":1476234,"uid":305360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T18:04:32.000Z","msg":"認同既，幫幫手投票，推到上熱門為止。